{"tid":916264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這是一溝絕望的死水","createTime":"2018-11-25T15:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T15:49:53.000Z","uid":96380,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e3f52276959ccd1e194d0fbcdecc9168cc32b9b3","tid":916264,"uid":96380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"這是一溝絕望的死水，<br />\n清風吹不起半點漪淪。<br />\n不如多扔些破銅爛鐵，<br />\n爽性潑你的剩菜殘羹。<br />\n<br />\n也許銅的要綠成翡翠，<br />\n鐵罐上鏽出幾瓣桃花；<br />\n再讓油膩織一層羅綺，<br />\n黴菌給他蒸出些雲霞。<br />\n<br />\n讓死水酵成一溝綠酒，<br />\n漂滿了珍珠似的白沫；<br />\n小珠們笑聲變成大珠，<br />\n又被偷酒的花蚊咬破。<br />\n<br />\n那麼一溝絕望的死水，<br />\n也就誇得上幾分鮮明。<br />\n如果青蛙耐不住寂寞，<br />\n又算死水叫出了歌聲。<br />\n<br />\n這是一溝絕望的死水，<br />\n這裏斷不是美的所在，<br />\n不如讓給醜惡來開墾，<br />\n看他造出個什麼世界。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過左差唔多一百年都啱用"},{"pid":"9c385348aa63c79863ad7f7f6cf6787bd931b69a","tid":916264,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T15:01:59.000Z","msg":"最尾個段改變左我既諗法"},{"pid":"7416ae82b60a0ee09ae4d4c27da4ea1413900a39","tid":916264,"uid":96380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c385348aa63c79863ad7f7f6cf6787bd931b69a","tid":916264,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T15:01:59.000Z","msg":"最尾個段改變左我既諗法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T15:05:09.000Z","msg":"咩諗法"},{"pid":"b1d41b387bfa7d5bd8e8c6d2a8484b0cf9b8f172","tid":916264,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7416ae82b60a0ee09ae4d4c27da4ea1413900a39","tid":916264,"uid":96380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c385348aa63c79863ad7f7f6cf6787bd931b69a","tid":916264,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T15:01:59.000Z","msg":"最尾個段改變左我既諗法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T15:05:09.000Z","msg":"咩諗法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T15:11:38.000Z","msg":"希特拉係啱的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d62badd7c455bc9b29a